John L Scott Real Estate Grants Pass

data.description: Here's your opportunity for that special property with a rural feel, that's just minutes from town.  This spacious 2200 square ft. home includes 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, with a bonus room/office.  Plus, the house is set up for split living with bedrooms separated on each side. The large primary bathroom has double sinks and vanities, with both a shower and soaking tub. There are two gathering spaces, both a living room and den.  The large kitchen has lots of cupboard space with an island counter/sink. There's also a separate dining room off of the kitchen and a dedicated laundry room.  Outside you'll find 3 and a 1/4 acres, tucked off of the road with a private driveway.  There are several outbuildings, an attached carport, and two areas set up for RV's. Listing agent is related to seller.
